Myspace activities have the following properties

    :created_at,
    :activity_id,
    :person_id,
    :text,
    :category,
    :object_title,
    :object_author,
    :target_title,
    :source

The following resources are instances of an activity.  In each case,
the "object_title" field contains the text with words to be counted.
	
    forum_posted
    forum_topic_reply
    share_item
    status_mood_update

A myspace_mood has the following properties

    :created_at,
    :person_id,
    :text
